  "about": {
    "hero_badge": "[ ABOUT RELOAD ]",
    "hero_tag": "About Us",
    "hero_title_1": "RELOAD",
    "hero_title_2": "Culture.",
    "hero_desc": "Reload is not just a clothing brand; it's a manifestation of deep dedication to streetwear culture. Born from a blend of high-level production expertise and bold vision, we are here to redefine the standards of street style through every stitch.",
    "hero_est": "EST. 2002",
    "story_badge": "[ BRAND STORY ]",
    "story_title_1": "Craftsmanship,",
    "story_title_2": "Collaboration,",
    "story_title_3": "& Culture.",
    "story_since": "SINCE 2002",
    "story_p1": "Starting in 2002, Reload's foundation was built on extensive behind-the-scenes experience in the leading streetwear and distro industry in Bandung. Armed with over a decade of flight hours mastering production details, garment construction, and quality, our founder, Agus Syahrudin, took a bold step in the early 2010s to give birth to an independent entity. The name 'Reload' was chosen as a symbol of powerful energy inspired by solid music culture.",
    "story_p2": "Our early journey was not just about producing clothes, but a strategic collaboration between two main pillars. By combining mastery in production with sharp promotional expertise from entertainment industry practitioners, Reload created a massive wave of enthusiasm in the market. We focused energy on building brand awareness and visual identity first, which proved successful in bringing an extraordinary surge of demand from the community upon its launch.",
    "story_p3": "Now, after going through various phases of maturation and a hiatus that provided space to perfect the vision, Reload is back (Reborn) with renewed energy. We remain true to our roots—presenting tough and iconic collections, from casual silhouettes to our flagship basketball-style jerseys—while continuing to innovate to dominate today's fashion scene.",
    "values_badge": "[ VALUES & PRINCIPLES ]",
    "values_title_1": "What We",
    "values_title_2": "Stand For.",
    "value_1_title": "CRAFTSMANSHIP FIRST",
    "value_1_desc": "Rooted in a production house that has served various legendary brands since the early 2000s, every piece of Reload clothing is made with a high level of precision. We truly understand the art of quality garment construction.",
    "value_2_title": "COMMUNITY & VISIBILITY",
    "value_2_desc": "We believe that a strong brand is built from communication and how you express yourself. Through solid campaigns and bold visual presence, we forge authentic connections with our wearers.",
    "value_3_title": "RELENTLESS ENERGY",
    "value_3_desc": "Inspired by our very name, Reload represents the power to constantly 'reload' passion and creativity. We are always ready to adapt and bring fresh innovation to every era of fashion culture.",
    "timeline_badge": "[ MILESTONES ]",
    "timeline_title_1": "Our ",
    "timeline_title_2": "Journey.",
    "milestone_1_title": "THE FOUNDATION",
    "milestone_1_desc": "Building experience, technical expertise, and reputation as reliable craftsmen and production house for pioneer clothing brands in Bandung.",
    "milestone_2_title": "THE INCEPTION & THE SURGE",
    "milestone_2_desc": "The Reload brand was officially formed. Through a combination of production vision and promotional excellence, the brand made its debut and immediately created a massive surge of enthusiasm.",
    "milestone_3_title": "PEAK EXPANSION",
    "milestone_3_desc": "Production scale was massively increased to meet the explosion in market demand, solidifying Reload's existence and capabilities in the fashion scene.",
    "milestone_4_title": "RELOAD REBORN",
    "milestone_4_desc": "After reflection and renewal, Reload is reborn with a more mature identity. Blending the legacy of past originality with a modern vision to once again dominate the streetwear landscape.",
    "team_badge": "[ TEAM & STUDIO ]",
